    <item>
      <title>Daily Security News from @trustpath - Mar 24, 2017</title>
      <link>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-03-24/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Mar 2017 18:05:01 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-03-24/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;New Yorkers See 60% Rise in Data Breaches in 2016&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An analysis conducted by the New York Attorney General&amp;rsquo;s (AG) office reveals a 60% increase in data breaches in New York in 2016. This resulted in &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.darkreading.com/attacks-breaches/new-yorkers-see-60--rise-in-data-breaches-in-2016/d/d-id/1328455&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.darkreading.com/attacks-breaches/new-yorkers-see-60--rise-in-data-breaches-in-2016/d/d-id/1328455&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Organisations struggle over which data breaches to confess to under new&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Australian Financial Review Laws will soon force Australian organisations to confess when they suffer data breaches, but deciding what counts as one is a challenge. Reuters.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.afr.com/technology/web/organisations-struggle-to-figure-out-which-data-breaches-to-confess-to-20170323-gv4w5t&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.afr.com/technology/web/organisations-struggle-to-figure-out-which-data-breaches-to-confess-to-20170323-gv4w5t&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;NY Data Breaches Soared To Record Levels In 2016, AG Says&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Law360, New York (March 22, 2017, 9:08 PM EDT) &amp;ndash; Fueled by hacks and employee negligence, reports of data security breaches impacting New &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.law360.com/newyork/articles/905081/ny-data-breaches-soared-to-record-levels-in-2016-ag-says-&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.law360.com/newyork/articles/905081/ny-data-breaches-soared-to-record-levels-in-2016-ag-says-&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Too many passwords and privileges key to data breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In a world of growing data breaches where enterprises are being hit constantly by phishing, malware and other attacks on all aspects of their &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.scmagazine.com/too-many-passwords-and-privileges-key-to-data-breaches/article/645892/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.scmagazine.com/too-many-passwords-and-privileges-key-to-data-breaches/article/645892/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;HIT Think Why insider threats remain the biggest risk to data&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; ransomware and hacking attacks draw the biggest headlines, it is actually improper insider access that causes the highest number of data breaches.  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.healthdatamanagement.com/opinion/why-insider-threats-remain-the-biggest-risk-to-data&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.healthdatamanagement.com/opinion/why-insider-threats-remain-the-biggest-risk-to-data&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;RDS-Knight Controls Device Access to Protect Sensitive Data&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Endpoint Protection feature incorporates a Device Control technology. Simple rules created with Device Control can enforce security policies and &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.digitaljournal.com/pr/3281312&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.digitaljournal.com/pr/3281312&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Payment Processor Secures Global Network with Stealthwatch&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As Stealthwatch collects NetFlow, it builds a baseline of normal network behavior. When a host displays behavior that exceeds thresholds of expected &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://blogs.cisco.com/security/payment-processor-secures-global-network-with-stealthwatch&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://blogs.cisco.com/security/payment-processor-secures-global-network-with-stealthwatch&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Balabit Co-founder and CTO Balazs Scheidler Honored as Gold Winner for&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yahoo Finance Scheidler is CTO and co-founder of Balabit, and the inventor of several IT security B2B software solutions that aim to prevent data breaches without &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/balabit-co-founder-cto-balazs-090000588.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/balabit-co-founder-cto-balazs-090000588.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Getting Another installation is currently in progress when trying to do&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Getting &amp;ldquo;Another installation is currently in progress&amp;rdquo; when trying to do an install of endpoint protection. By: ckandzierski. Created 23 Mar 2017 &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.symantec.com/connect/forums/getting-another-installation-currently-progress-when-trying-do-install-endpoint-protection&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.symantec.com/connect/forums/getting-another-installation-currently-progress-when-trying-do-install-endpoint-protection&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Honeywell introduces Pro-Watch 4.3 security management system for connected&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SourceSecurity.com These include third-party solutions including video management systems, physical security information management solutions, visitor management, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.sourcesecurity.com/news/articles/honeywell-introduces-pro-watch-security-management-system-co-2173-ga-npr.22661.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.sourcesecurity.com/news/articles/honeywell-introduces-pro-watch-security-management-system-co-2173-ga-npr.22661.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;How the dark web fuels fraud&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Data breaches receive a great deal of publicity. Recently we&amp;rsquo;ve seen arrest warrants for four specific hackers for the Yahoo! Breach. That&amp;rsquo;s a great step &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.itproportal.com/features/how-the-dark-web-fuels-fraud/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.itproportal.com/features/how-the-dark-web-fuels-fraud/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;The Top Ten Data Breaches of All Time&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To read this magazine feature you&amp;rsquo;ll need an Infosecurity Magazine account. Log in or sign up for yours below. Log In. Email Address. Password  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.infosecurity-magazine.com/magazine-features/the-top-ten-data-breaches-of-all/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.infosecurity-magazine.com/magazine-features/the-top-ten-data-breaches-of-all/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Data breaches in Russia soar as the country is increasingly online&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In 2016, the frequency of confidential data breaches in Russia increased 80 percent compared to 2015, according to a report by the Moscow-based &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://rbth.com/news/2017/03/24/data-breaches-in-russia-soar-as-the-country-is-increasingly-online_726981&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://rbth.com/news/2017/03/24/data-breaches-in-russia-soar-as-the-country-is-increasingly-online_726981&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Data-privacy regulator lectures Microsoft on law&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; and PIPs in government and various industries in developing a culture of privacy, and building resilience against data breaches from the ground up.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.businessmirror.com.ph/data-privacy-regulator-lectures-microsoft-on-law/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.businessmirror.com.ph/data-privacy-regulator-lectures-microsoft-on-law/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Data Breaches, Compromised Credentials, and Ransomware are Among CIOs and&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The thefts are so common because data can be as valuable as cash, according to IEEE Senior Member Zhen Wen, who discussed data breaches in &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://theinstitute.ieee.org/ieee-roundup/blogs/blog/data-breaches-compromised-credentials-and-ransomware-are-among-cios-and-ctos-top-concerns&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://theinstitute.ieee.org/ieee-roundup/blogs/blog/data-breaches-compromised-credentials-and-ransomware-are-among-cios-and-ctos-top-concerns&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;VIDEO: Outlook on EU Privacy Changes, Data Transfers&lt;/h3&gt;
